[/list]
If you test on other hardware, let me know!

[line]
[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]
Every feature is individually toggleable via [url=https://github.com/sonofskywalker3/GenericModConfigMenu/releases]Generic Mod Config Menu[/url] or config.json:
[list]
[*]Controller Layout (Switch / Xbox / PlayStation)
[*]Control Style (Switch-style or Xbox-style confirm/cancel)
[*]Console Chests (sorting, transfer, color picker, sidebar)
[*]Console Shops (A purchases, quantity control, sell tab)
[*]Console Toolbar (12-slot rows, bumper/trigger switching)
[*]Console Inventory (A/Y item management, bait/tackle)
[*]Console Shipping (A/Y ship controls)
[*]Console Menus (all game menu tab navigation)
[*]Console Furniture Placement (single ghost rectangle)
[*]Pickup To Active Row (NEW in v3.7)
[*]Suppress Right Stick in Overworld
[*]Carpenter Menu Fix
[*]Furniture Debounce
[*]Hold Start for Quest Log
[*]Bumper Mode
[*]And more
[/list]

[line]
[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]
[list]
[*]Stardew Valley 1.6.15+ (Android)
[*][url=https://github.com/NRTnarathip/SMAPI-Android-1.6]SMAPI 4.0+ for Android[/url] by NRTnarathip
[*][url=https://github.com/sonofskywalker3/GenericModConfigMenu/releases]Generic Mod Config Menu[/url] (optional, recommended — our fork adds controller navigation)
[/list]

